# DeepShield – Deepfake Audio Detection

DeepShield is a deep learning system designed to detect AI-generated voice deepfakes in Indian languages such as Hindi and Telugu.

## Problem
Voice cloning tools are increasingly used for scam calls. Most existing detection systems are trained on English speech and fail on Indian languages.

## Solution
Our system uses wav2vec2-XLSR and an anti-spoofing classifier to detect artifacts left by neural TTS systems.

## Features
- Real-time audio deepfake detection
- Support for Hindi and Telugu speech
- Confidence score output
- Spectrogram feature extraction

## Tech Stack
- Python
- PyTorch
- wav2vec2
- torchaudio
